text: Inzelga () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Belsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 389 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Krasnousolsky. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Inzelga
